HEADWORD: Lobeliaceous
<hw>Lo*be`li*a"ceous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to a natural order of plants of which the genus
<gen>Lobelia</gen> is the type.</def>⟦br⟧
